</span></p><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-141_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Casual wear:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Refers to a type of casual, comfortable and sophisticated clothing that is worn in contexts where spontaneity reigns because they do not require a formal dress code.</span></p><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-143_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Ethical practices:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">They are actions that combine values ​​and character to create a positive impact on life.</span></p><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-145_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Gen Z:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Also known as "centennials", it is the generation of people born between 1997 and 2010.</span></p><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-147_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Loungewear:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">It refers to clothing that can be used for moments of relaxation or rest, clothing that is functional and comfortable at the same time.
